<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Ramakrishna Mission Language and Culture School</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fff3e6;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #e65c00;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .header-main {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .symbol {
            margin-right: 20px;
            width: 150px;
        }
        .main-heading {
            text-align: left;
        }
        .sub-header {
            background-color: #ffd9b3;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .sub-header .subheading {
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .welcome-section {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
        }
        .left-side {
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }
        .right-side {
            flex: 2;
        }
        .welcome-section h1 {
            color: #e65c00;
        }
        .welcome-section p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .right-side {
            flex: 2;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; /* Center align items horizontally */
        }

        .button-container {
            margin-top: 20px; /* Adjust as needed */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center align buttons horizontally */
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 0 10px; /* Add margin between buttons */
            background-color: #e65c00;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff704d;
}


        .cta-button:first-child {
            margin-right: 10px; /* Ensure space between buttons */
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #e65c00;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
    <div class="header-main">
        <img src="/images/missionlogo.png" alt="Ramakrishna Mission Symbol" class="symbol">
        <div>
            <h1 class="main-heading">RAMAKRISHNA MISSION DELHI<br>
                <span style="font-size: 0.6em;">(A Branch Centre of Ramakrishna Mission, Belur Math, Howrah, West Bengal)</span>
            </h1>
         
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
</header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome-section">
            <div class="left-side">
                <img src="/images/Maa.jpeg" alt="Ramakrishna Mission Image" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;">
            </div>
            <div class="right-side">
                <h1>Welcome to Our Language and Culture School</h1>
                <p>At the Ramakrishna Mission Language and Culture School, we are dedicated to fostering a deep understanding and appreciation of language and culture. Our curriculum is designed to provide students with the skills and knowledge necessary to thrive in a multicultural world. We offer a variety of language courses, cultural workshops, and immersive experiences that cater to learners of all ages.</p>
                <div class="quote">
                    <p>"Education is the manifestation of the perfection already in man." – Swami Vivekananda</p>

                    <p>"Arise, awake and stop not till the goal is reached." – Swami Vivekananda</p>
                </div>
                <!-- <div class="quote">
                </div> -->
                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="/signup" class="cta-button">Sign Up</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 Ramakrishna Mission Language and Culture School
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
